==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Predicant
<hw>Pred"i*cant</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who predicates, affirms, or
proclaims; specifically, a preaching friar; a Dominican.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

